{"tid":288414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士擬售月票吸客 或設手機app留座","createTime":"2017-06-18T07:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T10:28:41.000Z","uid":20058,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5f4519caa23be5c2a1ff6c9189e12af48b386a9","tid":288414,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170618&amp;guid=56843777&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170618%26guid%3D56843777%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=zS8mjHy6ywoVYTmiwIoSbP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a9214832\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170618%26guid%3D56843777%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=2cff3ad5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170618&amp;guid=56843777&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會主席田北辰在電台節目透露，有專營巴士公司有意推出月票，惟政府對巴士公司的規限較港鐵高，有巴士公司認為不公平。田北辰認為，若巴士公司推出月票「全港通」，售價低於700元，相信會有吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n對於政府早前建議推行「優質巴士」，行駛新界至市區的長途路線，車上只設座位，<span style=\"color: red;\">田北辰認為優質巴士有吸引力，更透露有巴士公司或推出手機留座服務，「每朝早食完早餐未落街，就可以喺手機app訂下一架車嘅座位」</span>，相信不少市民願意乘搭。"},{"pid":"48d66aef782acf09a438912ec20954259cd25ecb","tid":288414,"uid":57797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:34:39.000Z","msg":"笑撚死，日日打交都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c97f853f84ea3df91dd9e0f2107451ed457e99","tid":288414,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:36:01.000Z","msg":"共享大髀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09dc667dd7fe60850fa60bcd5caace19b789fd6","tid":288414,"